dialogue.speaker: Dogbert
dialogue.text: HELLO. DO YOU REMEMBER SELLING SOME HAIR GROWTH FORMULA TO A BIG GUY NAMED DILBERT?

dialogue.speaker: Dilbert
dialogue.text: WELL, I'M DILBERT, AND APPARENTLY THERE ARE SOME UNUSUAL SIDE EFFECTS!

dialogue.speaker: Dogbert
dialogue.text: I TOOK TIME OUT FROM MY THRIVING LAW PRACTICE TO COME TALK TO YOU ABOUT IT.

dialogue.speaker: Dilbert
dialogue.text: THANKS DOGBERT, BUT I ONLY ASKED YOU TO GET MY PRESCRIPTION REFILL ... NOT THE DEED TO THE PHARMACY.

dialogue.speaker: Dogbert
dialogue.text: IN THE LONG RUN THIS IS MORE COST-EFFECTIVE.
